SYNTAX 1.3.6.1.4.1.1466.115.121.1.15{4096} SINGLE-VALUE )

attributetype ( 1.3.6.1.4.1.7914.1.2.1.12 NAME 'accountStatus'
DESC 'The status of a user account: active, noaccess, disabled, deleted'
