attributetype ( 1.3.6.1.4.1.7914.1.2.1.17 NAME 'mailSizeMax'
DESC 'The maximum size of a single messages the user accepts.'
EQUALITY integerMatch
SYNTAX 1.3.6.1.4.1.1466.115.121.1.27 SINGLE-VALUE )

